snippet.title: Strangers of the Power 3: Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Strangers of the Power 3 is the first 3D game by Tuomo's Games, taking full advantage of the 3D enviroments and the 360 degree camera for a fun and challenging gameplay.

Featuring stylistic, simple 3D inspired by JRPGs from the 90's and the early 00's, this game is a homage to the games that I was playing while growing up.


Subscribe to Tuomo's Games  https://goo.gl/3DgKZW
Steam store  https://goo.gl/abQCvN


■作曲：CAE_Bkr■編曲：CAE_Bkr■歌：みるく■歌詞：mieu
